    <title>SAP Build Work Zone (SAP BTP, SAP Build Work Zone standard edition, free plan)</title>
    <updated>2024-09-17T10:46:36.394000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Boris_Zezelj</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1686866</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;History of the problem:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;An app was developed in SAP BAS and deployed to Cloud foundry&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;The App was included in SAP Build Work Zone content, but it turned out that intent navigation was incorrectly configured (As per note 2965719)&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;The app was undeployed corrected in SAP BAS, then deployed again. This was done several times because semanticObject and action settings did not seem to take effect&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;At some point the content channel could not be updated any more due to error described below&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;At the moment the app is undeployed from Cloud Foundry but still shows up in content channel, without the semanticObject and action as in the first incorrect version&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The app is currently undeployed:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Boris_Zezelj_0-1726562716020.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/167282i728D62512BFA2DA2/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Boris_Zezelj_0-1726562716020.png" alt="Boris_Zezelj_0-1726562716020.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Error when updating HTML5 Apps content channel:&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Boris_Zezelj_1-1726562716035.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/167283i19D6B1B7BFD2D520/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Boris_Zezelj_1-1726562716035.png" alt="Boris_Zezelj_1-1726562716035.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Despite the error, status is set as Updated:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Boris_Zezelj_2-1726562716037.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/167284i8C6D474451429996/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Boris_Zezelj_2-1726562716037.png" alt="Boris_Zezelj_2-1726562716037.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;There is nothing in the report:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Boris_Zezelj_3-1726562716044.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/167285i440199AC0B3E9E41/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Boris_Zezelj_3-1726562716044.png" alt="Boris_Zezelj_3-1726562716044.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Downloaded JSON:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;{&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; "status": "SUCCEEDED",&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; "contents": {&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "total": 0,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "failed": 0,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "status": "SUCCEEDED",&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "messages": {},&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "correlationId": "844ad7fa-30c6-4fd6-58c4-6da0e3292ad7"&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; },&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; "reportId": {&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "contextId": "SUB_ACCOUNT",&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "subdomain": "sb9br8n12566y8fr",&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "instanceId": "SAAS_APPROUTER_HTML5_APP_REPO",&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "providerId": "saas_approuter",&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "contextType": "sub_account",&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; "identityZoneId": "66aa3fb8-d4b8-4433-992e-0aa841ced882"&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; },&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; "correlationId": "844ad7fa-30c6-4fd6-58c4-6da0e3292ad7"&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;}&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The undeployed app is still in visible in content explorer:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Boris_Zezelj_4-1726562716052.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/167286i5B91FB368D45DBA5/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Boris_Zezelj_4-1726562716052.png" alt="Boris_Zezelj_4-1726562716052.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Error when saving local copy of the (non-existing) original app:&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/sap-build-work-zone-sap-btp-sap-build-work-zone-standard-edition-free-plan/qaq-p/13867836"/>
    <published>2024-09-17T10:46:36.394000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
